prompt:
This is your last game of the experiment! First, you'll be shown pictures of items one at a time. For each picture, you have to decide if the item is typically found indoors or outdoors.

If you think it's usually found indoors, then press v key on your keyboard. If you think it's usually found outdoors, then press the n key.There will be reminders on the screen to help you remember which keys to press.

If you're not sure whether the item is an indoor item or outdoor item, go ahead and take a guess but try your best not to skip that choice.
